modName: Female Voice Replacer with Animated Prostitution sounds
descriptionHtml:
New video is up at http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ghGl-RZn_Sg

-------------------

Update: Versions 03 and 04 are up - volume has been lowered.

-------------------

Credit and thanks to JoshNZ (author of Skyrim AP mod) for allowing me to use his sound files in making this mod. I thought other female voices were either too cutesy/sharp/little-anime-girlish or just not sexy enough. 

Converting sound files to fuz files for Skyrim was really tedious work, much unlike Oblivion, but the mod is now here for your enjoyment. Be sure to turn down the speakers though :)

Check out the video on YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fb_-OOXMlo&feature=youtu.be.

Feel free to make any change and distribute as you see fit, but consider that this mod is possible only because the above author consented to the use of his files.

PS: If you do not like or in any way agree with this mod, it would be good if you could appreciate that there are others who do. Peace.
